metadata.name: Rug Radio - Genesis NFT (Signed by Farokh)
metadata.description:
This Rug Radio - Genesis NFT was digitally autographed by Farokh Sarmad at VeeCon 2022 on May 21st, 2022.

This 1/1 digital signature on the associated NFT was captured on an iPad Pro (5th Generation) in Procreate using the technical pen tool and an Apple Pencil (2nd Generation).

This Signed NFT is independent of the Rug Radio - Genesis NFT (Token ID #4569) owned by Kevin DeAngelis at both the time of signature as well as the time of mint and does not have any utility tied to Rug Radio, does not generate Rug Tokens, & does not represent ownership over the corresponding Rug Radio - Genesis NFT (Token ID #4569) shown in the underlying image.
